    pros: ["Intuitive interface lowers design barrier for non-designers, enabling rapid asset creation without training", "Brand Kit ensures consistent use of logos, colors, and fonts across all team members and projects", "Real-time collaboration supports live editing, commenting, and version history for cross-functional teams", "Massive template library (100K+ customizable designs) spans social media, presentations, print, and video", "AI-powered tools like Magic Resize, Background Remover, and Text-to-Image significantly reduce production time", "Seamless one-click publishing to Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn, and Pinterest directly from the editor", "Robust mobile app maintains nearly full desktop functionality, enabling on-the-go edits and approvals"],
